      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the lot! If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
