    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise suspension tuning across various driving dynamics. This 'mint' specimen retains its factory-fresh aesthetic, from the flawless carbon fiber roof weave to the pristine bolster integrity of the Novillo leather interior. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking a high-induction, high-RPM masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
