    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, preserved in showroom-ready condition since the day it was first purchased. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel lines up with factory precision, and the alloy wheels are completely devoid of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the premium sound system to the climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with a documented service history, performing exactly as it did on the assembly line with a smooth, powerful delivery and tight, responsive handling. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
